{
  "info": {
    "name": "Mini ERP - Auth",
    "description": "Auth module endpoints untuk Mini ERP Invoicing System\n\n## Cara Pakai\n1. Login terlebih dahulu untuk mendapatkan `accessToken`\n2. Klik tombol \"Authorization\" di collection → pilih \"Bearer Token\" → paste token\n3. Semua request dalam collection ini akan otomatis menggunakan token",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{accessToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1"
    },
    {
      "key": "accessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Login",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "login"]
        },
        "description": "Login dan dapatkan JWT token.\n\n**Expected Response:** 200 OK\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Success\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"accessToken\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\",\n    \"user\": {\n      \"id\": \"uuid\",\n      \"name\": \"Admin\",\n      \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n      \"role\": \"ADMIN\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"meta\": null\n}\n```"
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "if (jsonData.success && jsonData.data.accessToken) {",
              "    pm.environment.set('accessToken', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
              "    pm.test('Login berhasil', function() {",
              "        pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.true;",
              "        pm.expect(jsonData.data.accessToken).to.not.be.empty;",
              "    });",
              "} else {",
              "    pm.test('Login gagal', function() {",
              "        pm.expect(false).to.be.true;",
              "    });",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Get Profile (Me)",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "me"]
        },
        "description": "Ambil profile user yang sedang login (berdasarkan JWT token).\n\n**Requires:** Bearer token\n\n**Expected Response:** 200 OK\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Success\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"uuid\",\n    \"name\": \"Admin\",\n    \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n    \"role\": \"ADMIN\",\n    \"createdAt\": \"2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": null\n}\n```"
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test('Status 200', function() {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(200);",
              "});",
              "pm.test('Response memiliki user data', function() {",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.true;",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('id');",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('email');",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Login - Invalid Credentials",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"wrong@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"wrongpassword\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "login"]
        },
        "description": "Test login dengan credential yang salah.\n\n**Expected Response:** 401 Unauthorized\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Email atau password salah\",\n  \"errors\": null,\n  \"statusCode\": 401\n}\n```"
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status 401', function() {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(401);",
              "});",
              "pm.test('Error message sesuai', function() {",
              "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.false;",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.message).to.include('Email atau password salah');",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Login - Invalid Email Format",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"not-an-email\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "login"]
        },
        "description": "Test login dengan format email yang salah.\n\n**Expected Response:** 422 Unprocessable Entity\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Validation failed\",\n  \"errors\": [\n    { \"field\": \"email\", \"message\": \"email must be an email\" }\n  ],\n  \"statusCode\": 422\n}\n```"
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status 422', function() {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(422);",
              "});",
              "pm.test('Validation error', function() {",
              "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.false;",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.errors).to.be.an('array');",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Login - Password Too Short",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "login"]
        },
        "description": "Test login dengan password yang terlalu pendek (< 6 karakter).\n\n**Expected Response:** 422 Unprocessable Entity\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Validation failed\",\n  \"errors\": [\n    { \"field\": \"password\", \"message\": \"password must be longer than or equal to 6 characters\" }\n  ],\n  \"statusCode\": 422\n}\n```"
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status 422', function() {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(422);",
              "});",
              "pm.test('Password validation error', function() {",
              "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.false;",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.errors).to.be.an('array');",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Get Profile - No Token",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "auth": {
          "type": "noauth"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "me"]
        },
        "description": "Test akses profile tanpa token.\n\n**Expected Response:** 401 Unauthorized\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Token tidak valid atau expired\",\n  \"errors\": null,\n  \"statusCode\": 401\n}\n```"
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status 401', function() {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(401);",
              "});",
              "pm.test('Unauthorized message', function() {",
              "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.false;",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
